{"version":1,"content":"<html>\n  <body><img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20260423/s00024/6691e23f99024c0ab12f339bec4f544c.png\" style=\"max-width:100%;border-radius:6px;margin-bottom:1em\">\n    <p>天文台表示，與高空擾動相關的強雷雨區正影響珠江口一帶。預料短期內本港部分地區雨勢較大，呼籲市民提高警惕。</p>\n  </body>\n</html>","scraped_at":"2026-04-23T10:41:39.939503+00:00","quality":{"score":0,"chars":52,"images":1,"source":"明報 消閒","fallback":"none"}}